0b9fe\\n\\nThe original failing stage was `:compileTestJava`. Early Gradle runs show `RecordingApplicationClientProtocol` in `tests/src/org.apache.hadoop/hadoop-yarn-server-web-proxy/2.8.0/src/test/java/org_apache_hadoop/hadoop_yarn_server_web_proxy/Hadoop_yarn_server_web_proxyTest.java` no longer matched the expanded Hadoop `2.8.0` `ApplicationClientProtocol` interface and was missing methods such as `signalToContainer`, `updateApplicationPriority`, `listReservations`, `getNewReservation`, and `failApplicationAttempt`. The clearest evidence is in `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-server-web-proxy:2.8.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-09T18-49-35-510657Z.log`, `.../gradle-test-2026-05-09T18-50-45-465719Z.log`, `.../gradle-test-2026-05-09T18-52-07-111604Z.log`, `.../gradle-test-2026-05-09T18-52-32-053986Z.log`, and `.../gradle-test-2026-05-09T18-52-48-963421Z.log`.\\n\\nThere is also evidence that the compile fix itself was likely found: the later runs `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-server-web-proxy:2.8.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-09T18-53-35-995505Z.log`, `.../gradle-test-2026-05-09T18-54-41-324302Z.log`, and `.../gradle-test-2026-05-09T18-55-06-126436Z.log` all end with `BUILD SUCCESSFUL`, and the preserved candidate commit `132fb14f6c` on the preserved branch adds the missing test stubs plus a `2.8.0` entry in `metadata/org.apache.hadoop/hadoop-yarn-server-web-proxy/index.json`.\\n\\nThe most likely place the automation still failed was post-fix metrics/finalization rather than javac itself. `stats/org.apache.hadoop/hadoop-yarn-server-web-proxy/2.8.0/execution-metrics.json` records `status: failure`, `generated_loc: 0`, `artifacts.test_file: None`, and `artifacts.metadata_file: None`, and there is no `stats/org.apache.hadoop/hadoop-yarn-server-web-proxy/2.8.0/stats.json`, so dynamic-access coverage is still unavailable. The full iteration history is in `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-server-web-proxy:2.8.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-09T18-50-45-459143Z.log`.\\n\\nNext steps:\\n- Review the preserved branch and verify whether commit `132fb14f6c` is the correct passing candidate to keep.\\n- Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-server-web-proxy:2.8.0` and `./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-server-web-proxy:2.8.0` from that candidate outside the failed automation wrapper.\\n- Regenerate/investigate the missing `stats/org.apache.hadoop/hadoop-yarn-server-web-proxy/2.8.0/stats.json` so coverage can be recorded before promoting the change.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"turn.completed\",\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":377450,\"cached_input_tokens\":305408,\"output_tokens\":7433,\"reasoning_output_tokens\":3529}}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
